meta.name: Countdown
meta.description: The show in which two contestants engage in a battle of wits, competing against the clock in games of lexical dexterity and numerical agility.

videos.title: Episode 119
videos.overview: Colin Murray, Rachel Riley and Susie Dent host, with Nisha Katona in Dictionary Corner, as contestants race against the clock to pit their wits against vowels, consonants and numbers.
